                  "type": "text",
                  "value": "<h2 data-block-key=\"cpe6t\">In Page Structure</h2><p data-block-key=\"7otqv\">HTML can also be added directly under the body, generally don't use this unless you know you're doing something bad. for instance the <a href=\"https://openstax.org/kinetic\">kinetic</a> page is implemented completely inside an HTML block in the page body. this allowed kinetic to have a totally different design than what was supported by the CMS at the time.</p>",
